---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import teamPhoto from "../assets/team-photo.webp";
---

<div class="pb-50">
  <div>
    <h3 class="pb-5 text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">ABOUT US</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row">
      <p
        class="text-gray_text min-[2000px]:!text-3xl sm:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl"
      >
        AtomCraft is the world&apos;s first undergraduate-led project dedicated
        to designing, building, and operating a tokamakâ€”a cutting-edge fusion
        device that uses electromagnetic fields to confine superheated plasma
        and replicate the conditions of the Sun. Bridging disciplines across
        advanced physics and engineering, our multidisciplinary team is tackling
        one of the greatest challenges in sustainable energy: achieving stable
        and sustained environment for plasma confinement. By pushing the
        boundaries of fusion research, AtomCraft is training the next generation
        of innovators to tackle the final frontier of sustainable energy.
      </p>
      <Image
        src={teamPhoto}
        alt="Rows of AtomCraft team members lined up making gestures"
        class="aspect-auto w-full max-w-[1000px] rounded-2xl lg:w-[45vw] 2xl:w-[30vw]"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="mt-15 flex w-full flex-1 justify-between gap-10 md:mt-30 lg:mt-50 xl:mt-60"
  >
    <div>
      <h1
        id="members"
        class="gradient-text text-5xl font-bold sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl xl:text-9xl"
      >
        0
      </h1>
      <p class="font-semibold sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-5xl">
        Team Members
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h1
        id="teams"
        class="gradient-text text-5xl font-bold sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl xl:text-9xl"
      >
        0
      </h1>
      <p class="font-semibold sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-5xl">Teams</p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-fit">
      <h1
        id="disciplines"
        class="gradient-text w-fit text-5xl font-bold sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl xl:text-9xl"
      >
        0
      </h1>
      <p
        class="w-fit max-w-[90px] font-semibold sm:max-w-[100vw] sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-5xl"
      >
        Academic Disciplines
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  import { createCounterAnimation } from "../helpers";

  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    createCounterAnimation("#members", 63);
    createCounterAnimation("#teams", 8);
    createCounterAnimation("#disciplines", 6);
  });
</script>
